write

protected void write(Appendable _out)
              throws IOException
Writes all relationship specific information in the TCL update file. The relationship specific information are:
  • propagate modify flag
  • propagate connection flag
  • meaning
  • revision behavior / action
  • clone behavior / action

Parameters:
_out - appendable instance to the TCL update file
Throws:
IOException - if the TCL code to the TCL update file could not be written
See Also:
Relationship_mxJPO.writeObject(ParameterCache_mxJPO, Appendable)
